  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators test the hypothesis that fiberoptic intubation (time and success rate)
      differ between the Ambu® Aura-ITM and Ambu Aura GainTM in paralyzed anaesthetized pediatric
      patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
